Feeling.Later, I ordered 004-matcha, called sweet matcha, which is sweet but not too sweet. It is acceptable taste. The overall wine feels light, which is more suitable for friends with heavy taste and sweetness.
Part of the meal ordered the Ming Prince Oolong Noodle, Fried Chicken, Ming Prince Yam, French fries, chicken cartilage, dumplings, flowers, fish, and pig scalp.
